FIND-008 (MEDIUM): feedReducer.ts dead command branches
  Resolution: option (a) — wire shell through feedReducer command bus.
  FeedList.svelte now dispatches all user actions through feedReducer:
    handleRowClick → feedReducer(FeedRowClicked) → dispatchCommand
    handleDeleteButtonClick → feedReducer(DeleteButtonClicked) → dispatchCommand
    handleDeleteConfirm → feedReducer(DeleteConfirmed) → dispatchCommand
    handleDeleteCancel → feedReducer(DeleteCancelled) → dispatchCommand
    handleRetryDeletion → feedReducer(DeletionRetryClicked) → dispatchCommand
  DomainSnapshotReceived commands also dispatched via dispatchCommand.
  Components accept onRowClick/onDeleteClick/onConfirm/onRetry callbacks.
  FeedList passes callbacks to FeedRow/DeleteConfirmModal/DeletionFailureBanner.
  Reducer branches are no longer dead code.

